window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p>Chloe's quest to escape the Oracle's prophecy leads her to a magus with a secret: the eldren are not the only race to use magic in warfare. An ancient power is rediscovered, and a forgotten people will return. </p> <p>Meanwhile, cursed by his birth, Dion tries to forge a new life at sea, away from both the eldren and his former life in Xanthos, but the one thing he can't leave behind is his heritage. </p> <p>Two kings on opposite sides of the ocean prepare for war. </p> <p>The clash of civilizations has only just begun.... </p>"; 
